{"type": "article", "id": 19937, "title": "“艺妓”打蛋器", "description": "", "date": "2015-12-30T07:20:14Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 41, "image": "img/article/article_show/2016060615134487gc2lxyoIbVzXU5.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是一款打蛋器，它被设计成了一个折扇的感觉，月牙形，有扇骨结构。法国设计师 Serge Atallah 将它取名“Geisha”，是艺妓的意思，让人联系到折扇的优雅和灵活。打蛋器是用塑料制作的，可开可合，非常方便清洗，当收成一捆后就能直接放在抽屉里了。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150303utfM7sPxcJCSQhBX.jpg\" width=\"1050\" height=\"750\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.71428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150304Ys7vK2iPu1RMlBx5.jpg\" width=\"1050\" height=\"667\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.6352381\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150304yTdNW6gVnUFxDZ9X.jpg\" width=\"1050\" height=\"638\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.60761905\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}